aqucirer:
Acquirer na merchant side bank or financial institution. Customer payment request-a PSP (Novalnet) kitte irundhu receive pannum.
Adha Visa/Mastercard network moolama customer issuing bank-ku authorization-ku anuppum. Bank approve pannina response-a merchant kitte reach panna help pannum.
Successful payment-ku apram settlement, refund, chargeback, fraud monitoring ellam acquirer handle pannum.

psp direct why acquirer:
PSP (Novalnet) payment integration, API communication, fraud checks, payment method management ellam handle pannum. 
Aana card payment-ku authorization, Visa/Mastercard network communication, settlement, chargeback processing panna Acquirer venum.
Visa/Mastercard network-ku direct access Acquirer-ku dhaan irukkum. Adhanala PSP direct-a issuing bank-kooda communicate pannama, Acquirer moolama transaction process pannum.

Acquirer-oda main functionality payment authorization, transaction routing, clearing, 
settlement, merchant account management, refund processing, chargeback handling, fraud monitoring, PCI DSS compliance, reporting.
Simple-ah sonna, customer bank-lendhu merchant account-ku payment safely process aagi settle aaguradhu Acquirer-oda responsibility.
Card networks (Visa, Mastercard, etc.) generally allow only licensed acquiring banks (or licensed acquirers/payment institutions with acquiring capabilities) to submit transactions into their network. 
Therefore, an acquirer is required



Acquirer enna functionality :

Acquirer-oda main job card payment process panni, merchant-ku amount settle pannuradhu. Idhoda important functionalities keela irukku.

Functionality	Tanglish Explanation
1. Payment Authorization	Customer bank kitte payment approve/reject request anuppum.
2. Transaction Routing	Visa, Mastercard, RuPay, Amex nu correct card network-ku transaction anuppum.
3. Settlement	Successful payment apram merchant account-ku amount transfer (settle) pannum.
4. Merchant Account Management	Merchant acquiring account maintain pannum.
5. Clearing	Issuing bank-lendhu amount collect panni settlement-ku prepare pannum.
6. Refund Processing	Merchant refund initiate pannina customer account-ku amount anuppa process pannum.
7. Chargeback Handling	Customer dispute pannina chargeback process handle pannum.
8. Fraud & Risk Monitoring	Suspicious card transactions monitor pannum, fraud reduce panna rules apply pannum.
9. PCI DSS Compliance	Card payment security standards follow pannuradhu.
10. Reporting	Transaction reports, settlement reports, reconciliation reports generate pannum.

